{"tid":1733541,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"RTHK:  理大外示威者被制服後遭警襲擊","createTime":"2019-11-18T06:24:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T08:27:37.000Z","uid":79563,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"62799cc18f650daa4de066354b62917b0021c076","tid":1733541,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:24:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/video-gallery.htm?vid=1492934\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fvideo-gallery.htm%3Fvid%3D1492934&d=uhXF1s3LJRzyxl6IDZpy2cemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=64fc714f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fvideo-gallery.htm%3Fvid%3D1492934&h=fe4f33bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/video-gallery.htm?vid=1492934</a><br />\n<br />\n2019-11-18 HKT 12:05<br />\n清晨五點半，大批防暴警員在暢運道制服多人，有人被按在地上時，被警員以拳頭、警棍及長槍打，有人被帶走時血流披面。<br />\n<br />\n大批防暴警察在清晨約5時半，從暢運道攻入理工大學。原本在校園外與警方對峙的示威者，退到校園範圍。有人在A座附近的高位發射弓箭，有人投擲多枚汽油彈，A座一帶火光熊熊，校園內有雜物起火，火勢猛烈，冒出濃煙。<br />\n<br />\n防暴警察其後退到校園外，在暢運道與科學館道交界聚集，不斷向A座發射橡膠子彈和催淚彈。"},{"pid":"5b05ff236b9b4b39fdb2ce26e4023a36adf072aa","tid":1733541,"uid":222907,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:25:04.000Z","msg":"天真得只有你 令神仙魚歸天要怪誰"},{"pid":"212af5c1c306c37799609cf7ab290dae4e470848","tid":1733541,"uid":257780,"like":2,"dislike":29,"score":-27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:26:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0783f8c8c08349640f91113a740615ab174f42a","tid":1733541,"uid":9694,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"212af5c1c306c37799609cf7ab290dae4e470848","tid":1733541,"uid":257780,"like":2,"dislike":29,"score":-27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:26:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:36:34.000Z","msg":"咪男殺女姦囉屌你老母<br />\n而家咪有人聽你講出左黎投降囉<br />\n奶哂野啦"},{"pid":"6d9b9ee243221dd8541c288d07382cdb13dfc51f","tid":1733541,"uid":171718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep